<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">83倍速算法，83与某数相乘时，先将某数除以12为首商，扩大1000倍后，再加上余数与83的积，最后减去4倍的首商值，即为其积。可用公式</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">(12n+a)×83=n×1000+a×83-4n</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">进行速算，其中某数为12n+a（n为任意正整数，a为等于、大于零而小于12的整数）。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">83×29=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black"> 83×29</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2×1000+5×83-4×2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2415-8</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=2407</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>